DatoFOR-2016-10-11-1279

Ikrafttredelse15.11.2016
EndrerFOR-2015-06-12-646
Gjelder forNorge
HjemmelFOR-2015-06-12-646-§3, FOR-2015-06-26-1153, LOV-2014-06-20-42-§11, LOV-2014-06-20-42-§12, LOV-2014-06-20-42-§14, LOV-1992-12-04-132-§25b, LOV-1999-07-02-64-§11
